{"type":"message","id":"71d6fb3c","parentId":"d057abc1","timestamp":"2026-06-01T07:30:51.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK — these are the existing sprite files. Now let me check what Telegraph URL these are going to come from. Andre said he'll share via Telegraph. But his message included the sprite generator source code as a blob, not actual PNG files. Let me check if there are actual image files coming or if I need to generate them from the sprite sheet generator.\n\nLooking back at Andre's message — he said \"New agent sprites are ready. I'll share them via Telegraph\" but attached the sprite generator TSX file. The actual PNG files haven't arrived yet. Let me check if the dev server is running so the sprite generator page works:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"1c012efd-9e37-405d-8949-ffa2b840dde4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://localhost:3000/sprites 2>/dev/null || echo \"not running\"","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \\\"%{http_code}\\\" http://localhost:3000/sprites 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"not running\\\"\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":345,"output":189,"cacheRead":112128,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":112662,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780299024621,"responseId":"gen-1780299024-lUMX5Vb7hLed4TQufxDA"}}
